<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17241</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洗礼日这天，国王和王后正在等待客人们的到来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27480</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>保姆站在他们旁边，怀里抱着还是婴儿的小公主。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27480</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“多么美好的一天呐！”国王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31106</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的朋友和家人马上就要来了！……啊，坏了！”他拍了拍额头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“艾格尼丝来了，我忘了给她发请柬！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 他向艾格尼丝挥了挥手：“欢迎欢迎，我的姐姐！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾格尼丝皱起眉头：“你忘了邀请我，但我还是来了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的眼睛闪着蓝色的光，“我绝对不会错过这个......特别的日子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73111</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王转身去迎接其他客人 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76443</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾格尼丝在王宫里一边走一边寻找洗礼池。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洗礼池是神父用圣水祝福婴儿的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾格尼丝走过去，站在洗礼池旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，大家都来到洗礼池周围，神父正要把杯子放入水中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就是现在！”艾格尼丝心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把魔法药水抛洒进洗礼池的水中，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108166</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后原地转了三圈，低声念了一个咒语：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125746</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>灵魂轻轻，听我命令！身体轻轻，空中飘零！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125746</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135349</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不压弯人的胳膊，只压碎父母的心！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135349</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143027</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哭着的婴儿突然咯咯笑了起来，保姆这时也惊讶地叫了一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143027</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她没有告诉任何人，现在的艾伦公主感觉比空气还轻！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>刚开始，没有人意识到出了什么问题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但在洗礼后不久，发生了一件奇怪的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>艾伦公主从保姆的怀里飘了出去！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173689</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小小的婴儿一边咯咯笑着一边踢着脚，在房间里飘来飘去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173689</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快来帮忙啊！”保姆大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177125</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186149</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个仆人冲了进来，保姆指着天花板：“公主飘起来了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189600</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仆人跑去拿来了梯子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189600</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>保姆爬上梯子，抓住公主把她抱了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>后来，同样的事情又发生了，这次是国王抱着公主。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207677</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真奇怪啊，王后！”他皱起眉头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207677</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我感觉不到艾伦在我怀里，就像......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>公主从他的怀里飘了出去，她笑着在空中跳起了舞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快来人呐！”国王大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>仆人拿着梯子跑了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235641</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他爬上去，用一个大夹子把公主从空中夹了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王转头，看着王后。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王倒吸了一口气：“公主太轻了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对！”王后惊恐地说，“公主完全没有重量！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>